Guess my Number pseudocode

Initialize changing variables

Create main menu

1. Play game

	Generate random number
	Ask user for bet
	Ask user for number while they have lives and points
	Award user if they are correct

2. Options

	1. Change range of number
		
		Shows current range
		Lets user change range
	
	2. Change number of lives
		
		Shows current live count
		Lets user change lives
	
	3. Change initial points
	
		Shows current points
		Lets user change points
		
	4. Return to menu
	
		Returns to menu

3. Credits

	Shows credits
	
	1. Return to main menu
		
		Returns to main menu

4. Exit

	Exits program